<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.209357>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2 – 5. Body venter of Horaeomorphus calcarifer comb. n. (2, 3) (abdomen removed) and Horaeomorphus eumicroides Schaufuss (4, 5). Abbreviations: bs — prothoracic basisternum; hy — prothoracic hypomeron; msp — mesoventral process; msv — mesoventrite; mtp — metaventral process; mtv — metaventrite; pp — prosternal process. Scale bars: 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/209357/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

